sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser (SPA)
    participant A as FastAPI (auth)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    B->>A: POST /api/v1/auth/login {email, password}
    A->>DB: SELECT user WHERE lower(email) = ?
    DB-->>A: user row (or none)
    A->>A: bcrypt.verify(password, hash)
    alt valid credentials
        A->>A: issue signed JWT (sub, iat, exp)
        A-->>B: 200 {user, token}
        B->>B: store token; attach as Bearer on requests
    else invalid
        A-->>B: 401 {error: "Invalid email or password"}
    end
